	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi heri de rebus aliis.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nunc nihil habeo, nisi quod has a d. <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p974" cert="high">Carolo Molinaeo</persName> (de quo in tuis, quid agat, literis quaeris) interea accepi, in quibus, quid agat et ubi, ex ipsomet cognosces, ut mihi non sit opus ea de re scribere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsi proxime quaedam de illo, quę an acceperis, ignoro.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Historiam pastoris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l869" cert="high">Transsylvani</placeName> ex parte nosti; expectamus illum hodie; ubi venerit, quę amplius cognovero, ad te scribam.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p3138" cert="high">Theobaldi</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p19">Achatis</persName> sui, causam habebo mihi commendatam.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De ministro comiti <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8098" cert="high">Georgio a Wirtenberg</persName> dando cogitabo; certe rari sunt tales <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galli</placeName>, qualem ipse expetere videtur.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cogitabo tamen de homine pio, docto, modesto, pacifico.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Interea tu cum tuis omnibus bene vale.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8011" cert="high">Gvaltherum</persName> nostrum expect[o]; expectat eundem <persName ref="p3241" cert="high">Trempius</persName>, qui te una cum illo plurim[um sal]vere iubet.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernę</placeName> 7. februarii 1553.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8018" cert="high">Ioannes Hallerus</persName>, totus tuus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p3429" cert="high">Viretus</persName> scribit se mox ad te scripturum; nepotem suum se non habere domi necdum illum quicquam certi cum d. <persName ref="p8033" cert="high">Beza</persName> constituisse; quamprimum autem hoc fuerit factum, eum ad te scripturum, meque ut huius te admoneam, rogat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Clarissimo viro d. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Heinrycho Bullingero</persName>, <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tigurinę</placeName> ecclesiae fidelissimo antistiti, domino et compatri suo longe charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="de" type="auto">M: <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p495" cert="high">Heinrych Bullingeren</persName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
